name: VR Bottle Shooter
summary: Shoot Bottles with different rifle and be a professional VR bottle shooter! Real Bottle Shooter game is Next-level shooting game for being master in shooting. Aim and shoot Multiple bottles with guns and win the strenuous game. Cross the difficult levels and enjoy being a bottle shooter VR in reality. Play like Professional shooter and complete all tough levels in Energetic way. Take the experience of being the ultimate shooter in the VR game.
